---
title: Szechuan Chicken Ramen Stir-Fry 3 easy steps to a delicious dinner
description: This stir-fry is loaded with colorful veggies and is ready in just 15 minutes! You’ll sizzle up dark meat chicken and toss with quick-cooking ramen noodles in a flavorful sauce made with miso, soy, Szechuan seasoning, and a touch of honey. Add bok choy, cabbage, and carrots, then finish with Sriracha and sesame seeds for heat and crackly crunch.

